      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and driving exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with no scratches or swirls, and the interior still retains that new-car smell with no signs of wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled garage. Buyers can expect a pristine driving experience with zero issues or upcoming maintenance needs.",
