    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, which exemplifies a harmonious balance of performance, aesthetic refinement, and proven reliability. This unit has been maintained with rigorous attention to detail, ensuring that its mechanical integrity and interior appointments remain in commendable form. Having successfully passed our comprehensive multi-point technical evaluation, this vehicle offers a sophisticated driving experience for the discerning professional. It represents a premier opportunity to acquire a high-caliber automobile that has been preserved with pride and precision.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
