      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the robust 3.6L flat-six M96 powerplant, delivering 320hp through a precise 6-speed Getrag G96 manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut with factory-spec MacPherson struts and multi-link rear geometry. Critical mechanical highlights include a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a recently overhauled cooling system featuring a low-temp thermostat and metal-impeller water pump. The Bosch Motronic ME7.8 engine management provides crisp throttle response across the rev range. While the exterior displays minor road patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical synchronization of the drivetrain and the linear torque curve offer a visceral driving experience for the discerning technical enthusiast.",
